{"tw": {"2799920": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "天才退魔師才不會屈服於觸手妖魔", "steam_appid": 2799920, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/3b56938ba212c049cfd592b525f09d55.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/226973a87bdff7753cdfec6c3653a255.webp?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自古以來就一直仇恨著人類的暗之眷屬，妖魔。現今也存在於這個世界當中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而……從妖魔手中保衛人類的人們也存在於世。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那些人被稱之為「退魔師」，從很久以前開始就持續著與妖魔的戰鬥。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「闇無真利（kuranashimari）」是退魔師名門家族，闇無（kuranashi）家的現任家主。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一天，真利救下了被妖魔襲擊的少女「相川日和」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那天之後真利就投身於追趕妖魔與其戰鬥，只為拯救被刻上淫紋失去退魔師之力的日和。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/3998e7f38698f314ab333eda437de542.webp?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/7c3877b7d35d268c30b0cfa05ba01092.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=380 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/7d7a8e7517b932bd35bc4e73ea5ee858.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=380 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/12d9b801846fb942605346399d629607.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=380 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/01dda7cfde871a38a0e6469db1e1df46.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/2ee3546cd782246151832dc13403b1e4.webp?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指令式的傳統回合制RPG遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >並沒有複雜的獨特機制，即使是RPG新手，也能很快上手遊玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・敗北H</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/5493fae23d2291d7a1a10da6034f1e8c.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在戰鬥中，真利的（HP）歸零時，就會敗北。然後發生被戰鬥對象的妖魔凌辱的「敗北H」情景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >後續中，只要淫亂Lv越高，真利就會變得越加放縱淫亂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，在部分的情景中，有被附加上特定的異常狀態的話，CG圖就會有所差異。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・事件H</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/2cc6839e4d0d51f2c59062b0310a7990.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地圖探索的時候，選擇有顯示出粉色的特定選項時，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些是會讓真利被色色，相反地有些也會觸發自己主動要色色的「事件H」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，在部分的情景中，有被附加上特定的異常狀態的話，CG圖就會有所差異。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然後，在真利達到最高的淫亂Lv3時，偶爾也會有發生追加的情景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・戰鬥H</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/ea5ddc92d47ad0611884f436cc07d6b0.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在戰鬥中，受到妖魔的攻擊時，真利的衣服有一定的概率會破損。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這種狀態下，只要妖魔進行H攻擊，就能觀看到「戰鬥H」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在受到H攻擊時，真利的靈力（MP）就會被妖魔吸收，快樂程度和淫亂程度就會上升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，在部分的戰鬥H中，被附加上特定的異常狀態的話，CG圖就會有所差異。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・快樂程度系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在戰鬥中，受到妖魔的H攻擊時，「快樂程度」就會上升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當快樂程度到達100時，真利就會高潮，並且會有1回合無法行動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是靈力會完全回復，另外最大靈力、攻擊力、以及巫力會上升1。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・淫亂程度系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/92062ea360b78236da9f70727a917f4e.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受到妖魔的H攻擊，敗北時受到凌辱，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根據選擇在事件中被色色的時候，都會提升真利的「淫亂程度」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >淫亂程度達到一定程度以上時，「淫亂Lv」就會提升，在H情景中，真利的反應就會產生變化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・狀態異常系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在所有妖魔中，有些妖魔可以附加異常狀態在真利的身上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受到這種攻擊時，會附加上「母乳體質」「妖魔寄生」等異常狀態。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被附加上這些狀態異常的話，除了在戰鬥上會處於不利狀況之外，特定的H情景也會切換成狀態異常專用的CG圖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/95aab2d5009e7eecb7b48230bfb5fbc1.webp?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滑鼠與鍵盤都可以進行操作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在戰鬥中，按下shift鍵的話，就會切換成自動戰鬥模式，再按一次的話，就會變回原本手動模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色情狀態與回想房間也都一應俱全。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game"