ph\" >在這種狀態下，只要妖魔進行H攻擊，就能觀看到「戰鬥H」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在受到H攻擊時，真利的靈力（MP）就會被妖魔吸收，快樂程度和淫亂程度就會上升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，在部分的戰鬥H中，被附加上特定的異常狀態的話，CG圖就會有所差異。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・快樂程度系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在戰鬥中，受到妖魔的H攻擊時，「快樂程度」就會上升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當快樂程度到達100時，真利就會高潮，並且會有1回合無法行動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是靈力會完全回復，另外最大靈力、攻擊力、以及巫力會上升1。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・淫亂程度系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/92062ea360b78236da9f70727a917f4e.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受到妖魔的H攻擊，敗北時受到凌辱，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根據選擇在事件中被色色的時候，都會提升真利的「淫亂程度」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >淫亂程度達到一定程度以上時，「淫亂Lv」就會提升，在H情景中，真利的反應就會產生變化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・狀態異常系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在所有妖魔中，有些妖魔可以附加異常狀態在真利的身上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受到這種攻擊時，會附加上「母乳體質」「妖魔寄生」等異常狀態。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被附加上這些狀態異常的話，除了在戰鬥上會處於不利狀況之外，特定的H情景也會切換成狀態異常專用的CG圖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/95aab2d5009e7eecb7b48230bfb5fbc1.webp?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滑鼠與鍵盤都可以進行操作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在戰鬥中，按下shift鍵的話，就會切換成自動戰鬥模式，再按一次的話，就會變回原本手動模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色情狀態與回想房間也都一應俱全。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "從妖魔手中保衛人類的人們，那些人被稱之為「退魔師」。主人公退魔師真利，在擊退色情妖魔的路上會發生什麼事呢？", "supported_languages": "日文, 英文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1767928161", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1767928161", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1767928161", "website": "https://072project.com/?source=steam_tentacledemon&amp;utm_source=steam&amp;utm_medium=tentacledemon&amp;utm_campaign=store_link", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 1 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2+ GHz Processor<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL ES 2.0 hardware driver support required for WebGL acceleration. (AMD Catalyst 10.9, nVidia 358.50)<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["けーわいけーわい"], "publishers": ["072 Project", "072 News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 32800, "final": 32800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 328"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "1", "description": "動作"}, {"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2024 年 11 月 27 日"}}}}, "us": {"2799920": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Talented Exorcist won't submit to Tentacle Demon", "steam_appid": 2799920, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/7acc2683264726100dadc6259dccdace.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/7df54c305f341d95a5fa8dc8157afbda.webp?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since ancient times, there have been dark beings, demons, that harbor grudges against humans. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even in modern times, they still exist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However... there are also those who protect people from these demons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They are called &quot;exorcists&quot; and have been battling demons since ancient times. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The current head of the prestigious exorcist family, the Kuranashi (Dark Void) family, is &quot;Kuranashi Mari.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Mari rescues a girl named &quot;Aikawa Hiyori&quot; who was attacked by demons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To help Hiyori, who has lost her exorcist powers due to a womb tattoo, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mari dedicates herself to the battle against the demons...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/97ef45c0096b0bcfe3b6e04865f22b63.webp?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/545cb0c3a835c924505bb2bdad6da70e.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=380 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/86fe3c59eca8c4827ddda6fc0d786188.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=380 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/f1d0f80eb62bf048efc86934016317fa.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=380 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/8f7e4f3ad1573943ab1862c36c04483b.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/b185aef474dff0c10588eebc8ce342ee.webp?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a classic turn-based RPG with a command-style interface. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The design is straightforward even for RPG beginners!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・Defeat Scenes (H-Scenes)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/5493fae23d2291d7a1a10da6034f1e8c.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If Mari's health points (HP) reach zero in battle, she is defeated,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and will be raped by her opponent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The higher Mari's Ero level is, the more explicit and debauched Mari becomes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, in some scenes, specific Debuffs will lead to unique variations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・Event Scenes (H-Events)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/2cc6839e4d0d51f2c59062b0310a7990.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During map exploration, choosing certain options highlighted in pink may lead to &quot;H Events&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >where Mari is either forced or asked to do lewd things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These scenes primarily involve interactions with humans, and similar to defeat scenes, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >the higher Mari's Ero level is, the more explicit her actions become. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Similar to defeat scenes, some events may have unique variations based on specific debuffs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Furthermore, if Mari's Ero level reaches the maximum of 3, additional scenes may occur.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・Combat H</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/ea5ddc92d47ad0611884f436cc07d6b0.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During combat, attacks from demons have a chance of breaking Mari's armor,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and once demons use H attack after that, &quot;Combat H&quot; will be triggered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When receiving H attack, Mari's Energy(EP) will be absorbed by demons, and her Ecstasy and Ero level will increase.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, in some combat H, specific Debuffs will lead to unique variations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・Ecstasy System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When receiving H attack in combat, &quot;Ecstasy&quot; will increase.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Ecstasy reaches 100, Mari cums and becomes unable to move for one turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, her energy will be replenished, and her Max EP, ATK, and SP(Sorcery ATK) will increase by 1.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・Lust System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/92062ea360b78236da9f70727a917f4e.avif?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When receiving H attacks, being raped after defeated, and doing lewd things in Events,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mari's &quot;Lust&quot; will increase.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Lust is at a certain degree, &quot;Ero Level&quot; will increase, and Mari's reaction in H Scenes will change correspondingly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・Debuff System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Among the demons, some can apply Debuffs on Mari.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When receiving these attacks, Debuffs such as &quot;Lactating&quot; or &quot;Infested&quot; might be applied.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These Debuffs will not only put Mari at a disadvantage in combat, but also trigger specific H Scenes that have unique variations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799920/extras/fc78901d1c4563752617d056c983579a.webp?t=1767928161\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operate with either mouse or keyboard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pressing the shift key during battle activates auto-battle. Pressing it again reverts the command.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ero Status and Memory Room are also available.</p>